OL,3,CFamily devastated by loss of 'kind'
OL,4,CDan from Swindon who died in M4 crash
OL,6,FThe family of a 32-year-old man from
OL,7,FSwindon who died in a crash on the M4
OL,8,Fsay their lives are "much darker"
OL,9,Fwithout his "light and sparkle."
OL,11,FDaniel Conway, known as Dan, died in
OL,12,Fthe single car crash on the eastbound
OL,13,Fcarriageway between Junction 18 for
OL,14,FBath and Junction 17 for Chippenham at
OL,15,Faround 2am on Sunday 30 November.
OL,17,FIn a tribute issued by Wiltshire
OL,18,FPolice, Dan's family said: "We are
OL,19,Fabsolutely devastated at the loss of
OL,20,FDaniel, also known as Conway or Dan.
