OL,3,CFamily devastated by loss of 'kind'
OL,4,CDan from Swindon who died in M4 crash
OL,6,F"He was a much loved son and daddy as
OL,7,Fwell as a family member and friend to
OL,8,Fmany.
OL,10,F"Daniel was known for his positive
OL,11,Foutlook on life, his infectious smile
OL,12,Fand how he was always able to make
OL,13,Fpeople laugh. Daniel was always kind
OL,14,Fand had a beautiful energy around him.
OL,16,F"We appreciate all the kind messages
OL,17,Fand cards, our lives are so much
OL,18,Fdarker now without the light and
OL,19,Fsparkle Daniel brought to everyone who
OL,20,Fknew him.
