OL,6,F"We now ask you to allow us time to
OL,7,Fgrieve privately while we navigate our
OL,8,Floss."
OL,10,FThe motorway was closed for most of
OL,11,Fthe day while investigations were
OL,12,Fcarried out.
OL,14,FA 29-year-old man from Swindon, who
OL,15,Fwas also in the vehicle, was arrested
OL,16,Fat the scene on suspicion of failing
OL,17,Fto provide a breath test/ drug wipe
OL,18,Fand on suspicion of causing death by
OL,19,Fdangerous driving.
